Subject: [PATCH] feat: enhanced admin dashboard with expense/real estate
 widgets + deposit account manager

- Enhanced /admin overview with portfolio value, equity, rent income, and expense KPI cards
- Added property value pie chart, expense trend bar chart, category breakdown, and health overview
- Added new Deposit Account Manager (Depositumskonto) tab to /admin/finance
  - Inspired by husleie.no and hybel.no deposit management features
  - Summary cards, searchable/filterable table, expandable detail rows
  - Status tracking: active, pending release, released, disputed
  - Interest accrual tracking per deposit account
- No schema changes, no existing functionality broken, no files deleted
